WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 1=

00:00:04.980 --> 00:00:06.580
(Xiaoyao Pavilion)

00:00:07.900 --> 00:00:10.020
(Blessed with Children.
Wishes Fulfilled)

00:00:10.780 --> 00:00:13.980
(Lady Liu, Marchioness of Yong'an)

00:00:13.980 --> 00:00:16.100
(Marquis Yong'an, Tianxuan Kingdom)

00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:17.140
Everyone,

00:00:17.420 --> 00:00:19.260
today is my son's
full month celebration.

00:00:19.300 --> 00:00:20.660
I am truly delighted.

00:00:21.180 --> 00:00:22.579
After ten years of marriage,

00:00:22.580 --> 00:00:23.940
I finally have a son.

00:00:24.460 --> 00:00:26.419
It is all thanks
to our ancestors' blessings

00:00:26.420 --> 00:00:27.739
and Her Ladyship's protection.

00:00:27.740 --> 00:00:28.339
Come.

00:00:28.340 --> 00:00:29.460
Let us

00:00:29.540 --> 00:00:30.820
drink to this together.

00:00:30.980 --> 00:00:31.699
Good!

00:00:31.700 --> 00:00:33.820
Congratulations, Marquis!

00:00:46.020 --> 00:00:47.540
What's going on?

00:00:48.220 --> 00:00:48.819
What happened?

00:00:48.820 --> 00:00:50.660
Why did it suddenly crack?

00:00:52.180 --> 00:00:53.380
What's happening?

00:01:01.780 --> 00:01:03.899
Isn't that the jinx
from Marquis Yong'an's Manor?

00:01:03.900 --> 00:01:04.980
Why is she here?

00:01:09.580 --> 00:01:10.019
Father!

00:01:10.020 --> 00:01:10.539
Mother!

00:01:10.540 --> 00:01:11.600
It's my little brother's
full month celebration.

00:01:11.600 --> 00:01:13.659
(Suisui, Young Mistress)
How could his sister miss it?

00:01:13.660 --> 00:01:15.200
(of the Mystic Crow Clan)
I'm here to congratulate you all.

00:01:17.060 --> 00:01:17.940
What...

00:01:18.740 --> 00:01:20.260
Weren't you left at the mass grave?

00:01:20.460 --> 00:01:21.820
Don't come any closer!

00:01:22.060 --> 00:01:23.420
I'm warning you!

00:01:23.540 --> 00:01:25.739
I even asked eminent monks
to perform rites for you!

00:01:25.740 --> 00:01:27.260
No need for that.

00:01:27.380 --> 00:01:29.740
I'm here to take you with me!

00:01:59.980 --> 00:02:01.380
What nonsense is this?

00:02:19.900 --> 00:02:22.579
I am the young mistress
of the Mystic Crow Clan.

00:02:22.580 --> 00:02:24.699
Born under Heaven's blessing,

00:02:24.700 --> 00:02:26.379
I can sense fortune and disaster.

00:02:26.380 --> 00:02:27.340
But instead,

00:02:27.660 --> 00:02:30.219
none of you can tell good from bad,
or appreciate a sincere warning.

00:02:30.220 --> 00:02:32.939
For the past five years, I've worked
so hard taking care of all of you,

00:02:32.940 --> 00:02:35.780
yet you still threw me
into the mass grave.

00:02:35.820 --> 00:02:36.219
Fine.

00:02:36.220 --> 00:02:37.780
I'm done serving you people.

00:02:44.500 --> 00:02:45.419
Run!

00:02:45.420 --> 00:02:47.059
The beam's about to snap!

00:02:47.060 --> 00:02:48.960
That fool on the second floor
is still on the swing!

00:02:48.960 --> 00:02:50.640
The roof's already
been eaten through by termites.

00:02:50.640 --> 00:02:52.500
One more push
and the whole building will collapse.

00:02:52.540 --> 00:02:54.100
There are dozens of people inside.

00:02:55.020 --> 00:02:56.540
(What does that have to do with me?)

00:02:56.740 --> 00:02:59.140
(I warned them every single time.)

00:02:59.180 --> 00:03:02.380
(But afterward,
they still treated me like a jinx.)

00:03:05.360 --> 00:03:07.160
That man is clearly destined
for wealth and status,

00:03:07.160 --> 00:03:08.339
but sadly, he won't live long.

00:03:08.340 --> 00:03:09.780
What a pity...

00:03:14.660 --> 00:03:15.459
Meal ticket!

00:03:15.460 --> 00:03:16.660
No swinging...

00:03:24.060 --> 00:03:25.180
Indoors!

00:03:26.740 --> 00:03:28.159
And no hanging yourself either!

00:03:28.160 --> 00:03:29.520
(Xiao Heng,
Prince Jing of Tianxuan Kingdom)

00:03:30.840 --> 00:03:31.719
(Handsome)

00:03:31.720 --> 00:03:32.619
(= Long Term Meal Ticket)

00:03:32.620 --> 00:03:35.479
(Handsome means
a long term meal ticket.)

00:03:35.480 --> 00:03:37.700
(And that means meat
with every meal from now on.)

00:03:40.620 --> 00:03:42.500
Looks like the underworld's
having a hard time too.

00:03:43.140 --> 00:03:45.500
Even the Ox Head and Horse Face
are using child labor now.

00:03:45.700 --> 00:03:46.739
You're the ghost!

00:03:46.740 --> 00:03:48.260
Your whole family are ghosts!

00:03:48.860 --> 00:03:50.099
I'm human!

00:03:50.100 --> 00:03:51.540
A living, breathing human!

00:03:52.300 --> 00:03:55.540
Young Mistress, if you want someone
to take you in, you should act a little cuter.

00:03:57.380 --> 00:03:58.300
Hello.

00:03:58.340 --> 00:04:00.179
You're the meal ticket I've picked.

00:04:00.180 --> 00:04:02.340
If you refuse, I'll rip up the ticket.

00:04:02.460 --> 00:04:04.139
Then go ahead and rip it up.

00:04:04.140 --> 00:04:06.260
(What's with this meal ticket?)

00:04:09.020 --> 00:04:10.739
(That dark aura around him is intense.)

00:04:10.740 --> 00:04:12.400
(He must be plagued
by terrible misfortune.)

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:14.100
(No wonder he wants to end his life.)

00:04:14.620 --> 00:04:15.139
Quick!

00:04:15.140 --> 00:04:16.180
They're upstairs!

00:04:16.340 --> 00:04:18.100
I saw those crows fly up there!

00:04:18.500 --> 00:04:20.220
Catch that little jinx for me!

00:04:20.300 --> 00:04:23.320
How dare she play tricks and scare me!
Today I'll burn her alive no matter what!

00:04:23.320 --> 00:04:23.700
Get her!

00:04:26.060 --> 00:04:27.339
They're coming to catch me.

00:04:27.340 --> 00:04:28.499
Help me deal with them.

00:04:28.500 --> 00:04:30.100
Consider it repayment
for saving your life.

00:04:31.620 --> 00:04:32.339
Little jinx!

00:04:32.340 --> 00:04:33.540
Let's see where you can run now!

00:04:35.060 --> 00:04:35.620
Prince...

00:04:36.140 --> 00:04:37.300
Your Highness.

00:04:42.260 --> 00:04:44.179
Dear, who is he?

00:04:44.180 --> 00:04:45.340
Why are you kneeling to him?

00:04:45.620 --> 00:04:46.820
Shut your mouth!

00:04:50.180 --> 00:04:52.460
Three years ago, during the battle
at the northern border,

00:04:52.700 --> 00:04:54.500
all thirty thousand soldiers
were wiped out.

00:04:55.020 --> 00:04:56.940
It was all because
of this jinx, Xiao Heng.

00:04:57.140 --> 00:04:58.099
They say

00:04:58.100 --> 00:05:00.900
after losing his leg,
he became violent and unpredictable.

00:05:02.260 --> 00:05:04.380
Anyone who gets close to him
ends up unlucky.

00:05:06.860 --> 00:05:08.660
(Prince Jing...)

00:05:08.940 --> 00:05:11.139
(No wonder
his golden aura is so strong.)

00:05:11.140 --> 00:05:12.660
(So he's royalty.)

00:05:12.780 --> 00:05:15.520
(Isn't this far better than
that useless marquis manor?)

00:05:15.520 --> 00:05:17.480
(If I stay with him,
I'll live in comfort and eat well.)

00:05:17.480 --> 00:05:18.820
(Who would still dare bully me?)

00:05:23.900 --> 00:05:25.460
I am leaving.

00:05:26.020 --> 00:05:27.380
Move aside.

00:05:28.700 --> 00:05:29.700
Did you hear him?

00:05:29.740 --> 00:05:30.659
Move aside, all of you!

00:05:30.660 --> 00:05:31.939
My friend's about to...

00:05:31.940 --> 00:05:33.900
When did I ever say

00:05:35.540 --> 00:05:36.940
I was taking you with me?

00:05:48.760 --> 00:05:52.079
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:05:52.080 --> 00:05:55.919
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:05:55.920 --> 00:05:59.439
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:05:59.440 --> 00:06:02.410
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:06:03.280 --> 00:06:06.939
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:06:06.940 --> 00:06:10.690
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:06:10.760 --> 00:06:14.069
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:06:14.070 --> 00:06:18.120
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:06:23.720 --> 00:06:27.399
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:06:27.400 --> 00:06:31.039
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:06:31.040 --> 00:06:34.759
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:06:34.760 --> 00:06:38.399
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:06:38.400 --> 00:06:42.079
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:06:42.080 --> 00:06:43.999
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:50.200
♪Good fortune♪